    <h1 class="ed-title">Lake Hartwell</h1>
    <p class="ed-deck">A 5,000 sq ft lakefront house on Lake Hartwell, near the Georgia/South Carolina border. Five nights, a private covered dock, and room for a big group.</p>
  </header>

