  <!-- Food & supplies -->
  <section class="ed-section">
    <div class="ed-section-head"><h2>Food &amp; supplies</h2><div class="aside">In Hartwell, ~20 min</div></div>
    <div class="ed-prose">
      <p>The house is out on the lake, so town is about a 20-minute drive. Worth one big grocery run on the way in. A few places we'd point you to:</p>
    </div>

    <h3 class="ed-subhead">Groceries &amp; supplies</h3>
    <ul class="ed-2col-list">
      <li><span class="lbl"><a class="ed-link" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/Ingles+1000+E+Franklin+St+Hartwell+GA" target="_blank">Ingles Market</a></span><span class="note">Full grocery store. Open early to late. Best for a big stock-up run.</span></li>
      <li><span class="lbl"><a class="ed-link" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/Walmart+1572+Anderson+Hwy+Hartwell+GA" target="_blank">Walmart Supercenter</a></span><span class="note">Groceries plus anything else you forgot to pack.</span></li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="ed-subhead">Eating out</h3>
    <ul class="ed-2col-list">
      <li><span class="lbl"><a class="ed-link" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/Boat+House+Grill+149+Hartwell+Marina+Dr+Hartwell+GA" target="_blank">Boat House Grill</a></span><span class="note">Waterfront bar and grill at the marina. Come by boat or car, live music on weekends. Seasonal.</span></li>
      <li><span class="lbl"><a class="ed-link" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/Downtown+Cafe+63+Depot+St+Hartwell+GA" target="_blank">Downtown Cafe</a></span><span class="note">Longtime local spot downtown, Greek and Italian. Reservations a good idea.</span></li>
      <li><span class="lbl"><a class="ed-link" href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/Backstreet+BBQ+290+W+Franklin+St+Hartwell+GA" target="_blank">Backstreet BBQ</a></span><span class="note">Casual barbecue in town. Easy dinner for a crowd.</span></li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- What to bring -->
  <section class="ed-section">
    <div class="ed-section-head"><h2>What to bring</h2></div>
    <ul class="ed-2col-list">
      <li><span class="lbl">Swimsuits</span><span class="note">And beach towels. The house provides bath towels only.</span></li>
      <li><span class="lbl">Sunscreen</span><span class="note">July in the South is hot. Hats too.</span></li>
      <li><span class="lbl">Bug spray</span><span class="note">Lakefront in July.</span></li>
      <li><span class="lbl">Fishing gear</span><span class="note">If you have it. Otherwise rent on the boat.</span></li>
      <li><span class="lbl">Snacks</span><span class="note">Nearest stores are ~20 min away.</span></li>
      <li><span class="lbl">Cooler</span><span class="note">For the dock and the pontoon.</span></li>
      <li><span class="lbl">Flashlights</span><span class="note">For the walk down to the dock at night.</span></li>
      <li><span class="lbl">Games</span><span class="note">The house has some; bring favorites for downtime.</span></li>
    </ul>
